and I keep letting you do it.

05:50.283 --> 05:52.853
I don't know why
I keep letting you do it.

05:52.953 --> 05:55.188
What, you think I don't know
every fucking move you make?

05:55.288 --> 05:56.590
I don't want you near me.

05:58.058 --> 06:00.494
Fine. Play the victim.

06:00.594 --> 06:02.696
You're gonna
have to deal with me

06:02.796 --> 06:04.965
'cause I have a responsibility
to put your ass on the stand.

06:10.638 --> 06:12.105
Just take me to the nearest
police station.

06:15.008 --> 06:17.878
*

06:26.420 --> 06:29.857
OFFICIAL:
We have reason to suspect
that your guardian, Bria Jones

06:29.957 --> 06:31.358
kept you in custody

06:31.459 --> 06:33.461
as a means to secure
her own financial gain.

06:35.362 --> 06:36.630
I don't understand.

06:38.966 --> 06:40.133
OFFICIAL:
Shortly before you
and Bria were placed

06:40.233 --> 06:41.401
into witness protection

06:41.502 --> 06:44.438
your father set up
numerous trusts in your name

06:44.538 --> 06:45.806
as the beneficiary.

06:47.407 --> 06:49.409
Not only is Bria the trustee

06:49.510 --> 06:51.111
and in control
of the accounts...

06:52.713 --> 06:54.648
...she's a beneficiary
alongside you.

06:57.985 --> 07:01.989
So, you think that's why
she took me with her?

07:03.891 --> 07:04.958
For money?

07:07.861 --> 07:09.530
OFFICIAL:
Look, I know this is hard

07:09.630 --> 07:11.198
it's my job
to figure it out, okay?

07:12.866 --> 07:14.468
So I need you to be
honest with me.

07:16.670 --> 07:18.038
I just want you to be safe.
Nobody's gonna hurt you.

07:19.507 --> 07:23.010
Okay. Okay.

07:23.110 --> 07:25.946
OFFICIAL:
Has Bria Jones,
formerly known as Sarah Day...

07:27.481 --> 07:29.049
...ever threatened
your well-being?

07:30.484 --> 07:31.785
No.

07:32.953 --> 07:35.489
No. No, she hasn't.
She hasn't.

07:38.892 --> 07:39.927
No.

08:02.449 --> 08:03.717
Come up to your room.

08:09.923 --> 08:12.059
All right. Pack.

08:13.627 --> 08:15.763
- For what?
- Just pack.

08:15.863 --> 08:17.197
Pack like you're never coming
back here. Just pack.

08:18.999 --> 08:21.068
I don't need anything.
There's nothing to pack.

08:25.138 --> 08:26.139
Come on.

08:28.408 --> 08:30.277
Come on.

08:30.377 --> 08:31.545
I need you to clean up.

08:33.180 --> 08:36.049
[ water gurgling ]

08:37.417 --> 08:39.452
No, I can't do anything
with these on.

08:39.553 --> 08:41.221
Fucking get in.

08:41.321 --> 08:43.523
[ sobbing ]

08:57.337 --> 08:58.238
I'm sorry, Bria.

08:59.573 --> 09:00.741
I have to do this.

09:04.912 --> 09:05.913
And I didn't mean, I...

09:07.715 --> 09:10.483
I don't mean to say
hurtful things to you

09:10.584 --> 09:14.121
but you keep lying

09:14.221 --> 09:15.756
and pushing me around and...

09:17.825 --> 09:20.060
You don't understand the
position that that puts me in.

09:22.963 --> 09:25.833
I put my job on the line
for you. I wanted to.

09:28.702 --> 09:31.171
You don't, you don't seem
to appreciate that.

09:39.012 --> 09:40.280
I understand.

09:44.117 --> 09:45.085
Do you?

09:46.419 --> 09:47.354
BRIA:
I do.

09:50.791 --> 09:51.992
And I'm sorry.

10:11.779 --> 10:13.146
Here, put this on.

10:17.550 --> 10:19.152
Can't do anything
with these on.

11:20.714 --> 11:22.382
I wanna go away
with you, Ian.

11:25.218 --> 11:26.686
We could go
to the mountains.

11:28.889 --> 11:30.791
We could go to an island,
we'd just disappear.

11:35.729 --> 11:37.464
- I know how to disappear.
- I know you do.

11:40.667 --> 11:42.002
We should just go now.

11:50.243 --> 11:51.411
I want that.

11:57.250 --> 11:58.485
I want that too.

12:10.030 --> 12:12.732
*

12:19.172 --> 12:20.340
[ Bria gasps ]

12:36.323 --> 12:38.826
MAYOR:
The man of the evening,
Donald Fairchild

12:38.926 --> 12:41.261
invited us here,
and at some point

12:41.361 --> 12:42.762
you're gonna have to
get your checkbooks out

12:42.863 --> 12:45.198
so I hope you know
you're not getting off the hook.

12:45.298 --> 12:47.134
But for now,
let's welcome the man

12:47.234 --> 12:50.537
who's welcomed us into his home
to raise funds for IDC.

12:50.637 --> 12:52.139
Something I know
you all understand

12:52.239 --> 12:55.108
will greatly help our men
and women who've served.

12:55.208 --> 12:57.410
Donald, would you like to take
the stage in your living room?

12:57.510 --> 12:58.879
[ laughing ]

13:02.682 --> 13:03.951
- Hi.
- Hi, there.

13:04.918 --> 13:06.453
Sarah, hi.

13:06.553 --> 13:09.389
[ indistinct chatter ]

13:14.862 --> 13:16.997
Red or white?

13:17.097 --> 13:18.832
[ indistinct chatter ]

13:24.905 --> 13:25.839
Who told...

13:25.939 --> 13:27.340
I don't know.

13:30.610 --> 13:31.845
Who told, Sam?

13:33.446 --> 13:35.815
*

13:37.817 --> 13:39.419
Now, if what you're saying
is true

13:39.519 --> 13:42.289
then I can't have any of these
accounts linked to me.

13:45.158 --> 13:47.160
This states that you are
the legal descendant

13:47.260 --> 13:49.696
of Donald Fairchild,
and the beneficiary

13:49.796 --> 13:52.165
and trustee of
board of trust.

13:53.800 --> 13:56.503
Please sign here.

13:56.603 --> 13:59.506
DONALD:
Sarah, will you follow
Mr. Paulson home

13:59.606 --> 14:00.540
make sure he's all right?

14:06.146 --> 14:08.448
Samuel, I-I don't know
what came over him.

14:08.548 --> 14:11.484
Don't even talk to me
right now, Sarah. Just...

14:13.586 --> 14:16.423
[ indistinct chatter ]

14:18.158 --> 14:20.127
[ car engine starts ]

14:28.168 --> 14:29.269
LAWYER:
Katie Fairchild
and you are each

14:29.369 --> 14:31.071
entitled to 50%
of the trust.

14:31.171 --> 14:34.241
Katie on her 18th birthday,
and you're entitled

14:34.341 --> 14:36.910
to the, uh, full amount
of the trust, currently.

14:41.314 --> 14:42.983
And you understand
that Donald Fairchild

14:43.083 --> 14:45.018
has the right to monitor
any account activity

14:45.118 --> 14:47.921
until he's deceased
or rendered incapacitated?

14:49.256 --> 14:50.190
Yes.

14:52.492 --> 14:54.561
You know what you do.

14:54.661 --> 14:56.896
You know you want
to undermine me.

14:56.997 --> 14:58.865
I don't know
what you're talking about.

14:58.966 --> 15:00.533
Don't play dumb.

15:11.711 --> 15:13.846
TOM:
Like I said before...

15:13.947 --> 15:15.182
...front to back pressure,
like this

15:15.282 --> 15:17.850
and you are the safety.

15:17.951 --> 15:19.152
Never put your finger
on the trigger

15:19.252 --> 15:20.920
until you're ready to shoot.

15:21.021 --> 15:23.056
Keep your fingers clear
from up here.

15:23.156 --> 15:25.058
I don't wanna see you bleed.

15:25.158 --> 15:26.526
- You feel good?
- Yeah.

15:31.098 --> 15:33.066
- So like this, right?
- No. Um...

15:33.166 --> 15:34.567
I'm kidding, Tom.

15:36.903 --> 15:38.671
What time
does Donald get home?

15:38.771 --> 15:39.973
[ gunshot ]

15:42.642 --> 15:43.710
What would you do if I died?

15:46.479 --> 15:47.614
[ Donald laughs ]

15:50.783 --> 15:51.718
What's funny?

15:56.823 --> 15:58.691
DONALD:
Are we really
fucking doing this?

16:00.994 --> 16:02.529
Are we really having
this conversation?

16:04.097 --> 16:05.398
Could happen.

16:12.072 --> 16:13.073
DONALD:
What do you want me to say?

16:15.108 --> 16:17.610
That I'd be devastated?

16:27.720 --> 16:29.156
What would you do if I died?

16:31.524 --> 16:32.959
I'd be devastated.

16:33.060 --> 16:34.561
[ laughing ]

16:41.568 --> 16:43.270
But you're the kind of man
that dies.

16:43.370 --> 16:44.337
Oh.

16:46.839 --> 16:48.575
[ clears throat ]
Of course I'll die.

16:49.942 --> 16:53.246
That's the way life works, dear.

17:01.054 --> 17:02.189
[ sighs ]

17:10.863 --> 17:12.765
IAN:
Yeah. How far to the
courthouse, my good man?

17:12.865 --> 17:15.135
DRIVER:
We're only a few minutes away.
You need something?

17:15.235 --> 17:17.270
IAN:
I just gotta take a leak.
That's all.

17:17.370 --> 17:19.139
- Where are you dropping us?
- The back entrance.

17:19.239 --> 17:21.141
There's a bathroom two doors
down from the entrance

17:21.241 --> 17:22.342
so not long.

17:23.610 --> 17:26.479
*

17:56.643 --> 17:59.512
*

18:29.742 --> 18:32.612
*

18:52.765 --> 18:55.635
*

18:58.171 --> 18:59.439
[ elevator dings ]

19:10.283 --> 19:12.185
DEFENSE LAWYER:
Given the recent evidence
provided by the court

19:12.285 --> 19:14.421
and my client,
that the witness

19:14.521 --> 19:16.022
you're about to see has been
deemed the legal descendant

19:16.122 --> 19:17.089
of Donald Fairchild

19:17.190 --> 19:19.626
she should not be forced
to testify.

19:19.726 --> 19:21.661
PROSECUTION LAWYER:
There is proof and testimony

19:21.761 --> 19:24.063
that the witness
we're about to see has had

19:24.163 --> 19:25.832
sexual relations
with Donald Fairchild.

19:25.932 --> 19:28.268
Therefore, she is in violation

19:28.368 --> 19:30.670
of the statute prohibiting
intercourse with anyone

19:30.770 --> 19:33.573
with whom they share
lineal consanguinity.

19:33.673 --> 19:36.209
JUDGE:
Given these bizarre
circumstances, I understand

19:36.309 --> 19:38.311
but the witness
is not protected

19:38.411 --> 19:39.712
under any national law.

19:39.812 --> 19:42.482
- Motion denied.
- Thank you, Your Honor.

19:42.582 --> 19:44.284
I'll risk everything
right now.

19:49.922 --> 19:51.324
Blink if you'll
come with me.

19:54.394 --> 19:56.296
[ door opens ]

19:56.396 --> 19:57.664
COURT CLERK:
Sarah Day.

20:01.067 --> 20:02.435
That's you.

20:11.344 --> 20:12.812
[ sniffles ]

20:12.912 --> 20:15.748
[ indistinct chatter ]

20:22.121 --> 20:23.723
COURT CLERK:
Please stand.

20:23.823 --> 20:24.791
Raise your right hand.

20:26.393 --> 20:27.727
Do you solemnly affirm
to tell the truth

20:27.827 --> 20:29.296
the whole truth,
and nothing but the truth

20:29.396 --> 20:31.664
under pains and penalties
of perjury?

20:31.764 --> 20:33.700
- I do.
- Please be seated.

20:35.802 --> 20:36.969
JUDGE:
Prosecution, your witness.

20:39.906 --> 20:41.574
Please state your name
for the record.

20:47.280 --> 20:49.549
Please state your name
for the record.

20:58.558 --> 21:01.394
[ breathing heavily ]

21:17.109 --> 21:18.711
I need...

21:23.450 --> 21:24.851
I'm sorry,
can you speak louder?

21:26.152 --> 21:28.355
I need a minute to myself.
I'm...

21:30.122 --> 21:31.891
Just not,
I'm not feeling well.

21:33.526 --> 21:34.961
Fifteen minutes, okay?

21:39.632 --> 21:41.934
The witness needs a moment.
We'll take a 15-minute recess.

21:58.785 --> 22:00.319
[ retches ]

22:01.921 --> 22:03.055
[ coughs ]

22:18.838 --> 22:19.872
[ sighs ]

22:33.285 --> 22:34.621
[ door opens ]

22:34.721 --> 22:37.557
[ footsteps approaching ]

22:40.493 --> 22:41.728
[ door opens ]

22:42.929 --> 22:45.832
*

